social_posts.post_text:
Good morning my dears! ❤️ 
I called back to Poland, rested and slept off.
I would like to thank you all for your tremendous support and kindness that I have received from you 🤗
I am proud and happy that I qualified for the Top 20 of the Miss Charm competition and I also bring with me the title of Top 5 in swimsuit competition 🏆
This trip was a great experience for me. It was hard work and it required a lot of perseverance, courage and discipline from me. I overcame many of my weaknesses and gained self-confidence. I feel stronger now and this experience has taught me a lot. I will bring with me a lot of beautiful memories, I have new friends with whom I am in constant contact and I am very grateful that I met them. I would like to thank the Miss Polonia organization for their help in the preparations and support during the entire stay in Vietnam 🥰

Duet BLUE RETINOL od @biotherm 

Lekki krem z retinolem nawilża skórę i dostarcza jej ważnych składników odżywczych. Bogata formuła kremu znacząco poprawia jej stan. Przeciwdziała powstawaniu zmarszczek i drobnych lini, jednocześnie stymulując odnowe komórkową. Bardzo dobrze nadaje sie pod makijaż.
Serum na noc zawiera Blue Retinol, czyli połączenie czystego retinolu i naturalnego planktonu. Pomaga intensywnie regenerować skóre i widocznie poprawia jej kondycje.
